{"tid":1357974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗遊行一日未定好性質，好多和理非都唔會敢去","createTime":"2019-07-23T23:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:11:49.000Z","uid":8244,"like":85,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5132b70a8873cd74bd8ac44cf3bd4be3b5226f5e","tid":1357974,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"覺得成個活動無可避免需要大量人手<br />\n所以對外宣傳都係要以遊行做主打 （可以叫大家準備memo紙又好點都好）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但唔好去之前就講到明乜野燒村拆祠堂咁</span><br />\n到時前線做咪做，都係平時咁各有各做<br />\n事前張揚 令和理非唔敢膽一齊黎，差佬同班垃圾鄉黑又有防範咁<br />\n<br />\n過往咁耐既運動就算有勇武，都係對準個政權 或者 政權打手<br />\n真係唔建議搞無差別攻擊（燒村），咁只會變左同佢地一樣<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住去元朗一日可以消滅呢班人<br />\n佢地始終存在左幾十年<br />\n我地只係需要做d野落佢面<br />\n令佢地知道就算係元朗，都唔係佢地玩哂，同民意對抗就會有幾萬人黎你條村玩"},{"pid":"7da528cb265bcc5592c7600cbb9c907288c8ed95","tid":1357974,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0fa3b25db570e9705649c7e605c6fdc6d4e5eae","tid":1357974,"uid":44722,"like":3,"dislike":44,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e808a45163ecab1a24f6e5e5e37fb6cb00aa93b","tid":1357974,"uid":158008,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:52:12.000Z","msg":"燒村我一定唔去"},{"pid":"c29353ef8f68d9414a0ff2a55ac87a55e1137254","tid":1357974,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:52:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n元朗一役絕對需要更多計劃同關注<br />\n而家比分化同gossip搶哂fo"},{"pid":"d3944c9cdee55b7960473b70bd566f8836015acd","tid":1357974,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0fa3b25db570e9705649c7e605c6fdc6d4e5eae","tid":1357974,"uid":44722,"like":3,"dislike":44,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />膠都廢時比"},{"pid":"c2261ac3d4bbd623e7c9d764fb94d9d710bb91ca","tid":1357974,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:53:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a3940b435aa9088ccf3e78bd6434d1bc4fc8a1b","tid":1357974,"uid":8244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c1be1d1afc666257fdfb064a470c2c48b2366ea","tid":1357974,"uid":14494,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:56:16.000Z","msg":"岩 好多人上晒頭咁話唔燒村唔拆祠堂下次大西北就割席，心諗咩邏輯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正會行動既做之前都會諗咁做對場運動有咩好處越處架啦，唔通要好似黑社會劈友咁預告埋時間地點咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁做根本只會嚇到原本想去既人唔敢去"},{"pid":"f31586be24d176f3bf4582398c87cd2f01675122","tid":1357974,"uid":202383,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:56:27.000Z","msg":"由722開始睇左兩晚 我只係睇到<br />\n<br />\n一到凌晨時分就有一批人鼓吹人燒村拆祠堂<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會推721西環po<br />\n<br />\n晚晚都群魔亂舞係到吹風<br />\n<br />\n班人咩心態 自己判斷"},{"pid":"3ad4cce83a6a0c55e905e52aa9436029a72b7aa5","tid":1357974,"uid":124983,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:57:46.000Z","msg":"唔好燒村搞祠堂 唔好令和理非唔敢出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dc8388278fd3d7cf2669f7a430636a59bb4a41","tid":1357974,"uid":34705,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"和平遊行，但俾人搞我哋會全力反擊"},{"pid":"6f4e17d3e01e6f9ee831da629d603de15656d73a","tid":1357974,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ad4cce83a6a0c55e905e52aa9436029a72b7aa5","tid":1357974,"uid":124983,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:57:46.000Z","msg":"唔好燒村搞祠堂 唔好令和理非唔敢出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm